caption: Long wait but really good food

Food is amazing, service was pretty awful, manager or owner , was atrocious, I mean we went with a party of 6, and we didn’t complain that we waited 2 hours and only were served one round of drinks or didn’t get our food for 2 hours, but we did complain when the birthday girl didn’t get her food until all of us were done eating .  We understood they were short staffed, but laughing in her face when she was upset about it probably wasn’t the solution.  And then berating her and telling her (because she’s also in the food industry) that he hopes this doesn’t affect her work ethic was pretty wild.  If you forget someone’s order you would normally apologize , not act like it was our fault.  Again the food was amazing , the manager or owner , was just really bad at his job , probably had to do with his “terrible work ethic”.  Come at your own risk.
